          "comment": "All checklist items pass. Store, panel, refetch, config types, merge, and public exports are all correct. One non-blocking edge case: stale in-flight fetch writes can land on a re-initialised store if initNetworkStore is called again before previous fetches complete — silent corruption but no crash. Dependency on the network object reference (not network.apis) in useEffect is consistent with the existing logs pattern. Build and lint clean.",
